<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="primary-adj">primary <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'praɪməri/    美 /'praɪmeri/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-main-prime">1.★ <strong>最重要的；基本的；主要的 (main / prime)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The primary aim of this course is to improve your spoken English. 
这门课的主要目的是提高你们的英语口语能力。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>初等教育的；小学教育的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>primary school</strong> 
小学</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>primarily /praɪ'merəli; 'praɪmərəli/ adv   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>In those days, our <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (主要的) concern was to provide people who were stopped by the snow storm with food and health care.  （2008 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. primary / main  </p></div>